---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Shelly Xiong"
  description="Shelly Xiong is a NYC birder on a Linnaean Society committee. Art, writing, and software for the city's birds."
>
  <main style="padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 40px);">
    <section class="section about" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>I'm Shelly. I watch birds in New York City.</p>
            <p>New York gets more migratory bird traffic than almost anywhere on the East Coast. Central Park alone sees over 270 species in a given year. I keep a public eBird profile and write about what I find across the five boroughs.</p>
            <p>I'm on a committee of the <strong><a href="https://www.linnaeannewyork.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Linnaean Society of New York</a></strong>, which has been around since 1878. I also volunteer with a few NYC birding organizations. A few of my photos have shown up in Linnaean field trip reports.</p>
            <p>The rest of the time I work in software (currently as a Website Administrator at the <a href="https://www.metmuseum.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metropolitan Museum of Art</a>; <a href="/work">full work history</a>). I draw a lot and I'm teaching myself risograph printing. Online I've been <strong><a href="/#contact">@shellylynnx</a></strong> for as long as I can remember, and I publish longer birding pieces as <strong>NYC Subway Birder</strong> at <a href="/notes">/notes</a>.</p>
            <p>If you want to get in touch about press, commissions, partnerships, or anything else, email <a href="mailto:helloshellylynnx@gmail.com">helloshellylynnx@gmail.com</a>.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-interests">
            <img class="about-photo" src="/images/shelly.jpg" alt="Shelly Xiong in front of a circular window framing the NYC skyline at sunset" />
            <h3>Credentials &amp; affiliations</h3>
            <ul class="interest-list">
              <li><span class="interest-icon">&#x1F426;</span> <a href="https://www.linnaeannewyork.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Linnaean Society of NY</a>, committee</li>
              <li><span class="interest-icon">&#x1F985;</span> NYC birding community, volunteer</li>
              <li><span class="interest-icon">&#x1F4F8;</span> Photography, published in Linnaean field trip reports</li>
              <li><span class="interest-icon">&#x1F4DD;</span> <a href="https://ebird.org/profile/NDQ0MjU4OA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">eBird</a>, public checklists (133 species)</li>
              <li><span class="interest-icon">&#x1F4BB;</span> Projects: <a href="https://shellylynnx.github.io/projects/METBird/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">METBird</a>, <a href="https://shellylynnx.github.io/projects/NYCoffleash/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NYC Off-Leash</a></li>
              <li><span class="interest-icon">&#x1F4BC;</span> <a href="/work">Work history</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
